articles.description: The CSS Color Module Level 4 specification defined a slew of new color features when it became a candidate recommendation in 2022, including Oklab and Oklch, which have widened the field of color we have to work with. articles.author: hello@smashingmagazine.com (Andy Budd)

articles.author: hello@smashingmagazine.com (Preethi Sam)

articles.author: hello@smashingmagazine.com (Costa Alexoglou)
